{"tid":297934,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"deadlift酸痛一問","createTime":"2017-06-26T01:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T05:46:26.000Z","uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2389d77f5d04974bd4f807a6831ca1ae8500bb53","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"本身做gym差唔多一年 但係deadlift同腳少操 前日就操下腳同做deadlift 做deadlift 嗰時大概做6-9RM到 完成到動作 跟住尋日開始下背開始痛 條腰彎唔到  側彎身都痛 訓係到就唔痛<br />\n我都知可能臨尾嗰幾下個姿勢唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問係正常酸痛定受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537953605405425bbcf03958d5b72a2efa800ea1","tid":297934,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身做gym差唔多一年 但係deadlift同腳少操 前日就操下腳同做deadlift 做deadlift 嗰時大概做6-9RM到 完成到動作 跟住尋日開始下背開始痛 條腰彎唔到  側彎身都痛 訓係到就唔痛<br />\n我都知可能臨尾嗰幾下個姿勢唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問係正常酸痛定受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抖一排先，下次再操時做返輕啲，硬拉背要直，郁髖關節用hamstring用屎忽拉，唔係彎腰伸直，操返多啲腳。<br />\n我真係唔係好明點解啲人唔操腳，明明日常生活最具功能性嘅一定係用腳多啲動作，你做得多bench press得嚟嘅成效就係可以做更多bunch press。<br />\n反而腳強壯嘅話，日常跑跳行搬重嘢都好有用"},{"pid":"89c4afdaf4512aba941074f2a1732bb50d3bd9d2","tid":297934,"uid":8097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"受傷<br />\n有機會係拉傷肌肉<br />\n肌肉過緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlower back永遠都要keep住直<br />\n發力點係腳發力先再慢慢到下腰同背<br />\n每一下core都唔可以放鬆 休息一排再做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再痛既話建議你去睇針灸"},{"pid":"666ba88549c5cd2acd728c1bdd3daf9cdf1fc358","tid":297934,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身做gym差唔多一年 但係deadlift同腳少操 前日就操下腳同做deadlift 做deadlift 嗰時大概做6-9RM到 完成到動作 跟住尋日開始下背開始痛 條腰彎唔到  側彎身都痛 訓係到就唔痛<br />\n我都知可能臨尾嗰幾下個姿勢唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問係正常酸痛定受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抖一排先，下次再操時做返輕啲，硬拉背要直，郁髖關節用hamstring用屎忽拉，唔係彎腰伸直，操返多啲腳。<br />\n我真係唔係好明點解啲人唔操腳，明明日常生活最具功能性嘅一定係用腳多啲動作，你做得多bench press得嚟嘅成效就係可以做更多bunch press。<br />\n反而腳強壯嘅話，日常跑跳行搬重嘢都好有用</blockquote><br />\n認同<br />\n小妹做gym都花一半時間係腳<br />\n發力好過以前好多"},{"pid":"cca1d6b9e452ac91f19bb5ecea5a47ad43b188fb","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受傷<br />\n有機會係拉傷肌肉<br />\n肌肉過緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlower back永遠都要keep住直<br />\n發力點係腳發力先再慢慢到下腰同背<br />\n每一下core都唔可以放鬆 休息一排再做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再痛既話建議你去睇針灸</blockquote><br />\n但係我嗰時做完唔覺痛wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係返到去一排先feel到"},{"pid":"dca3939aef825e7be7fec1e465ba3224463184e3","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身做gym差唔多一年 但係deadlift同腳少操 前日就操下腳同做deadlift 做deadlift 嗰時大概做6-9RM到 完成到動作 跟住尋日開始下背開始痛 條腰彎唔到  側彎身都痛 訓係到就唔痛<br />\n我都知可能臨尾嗰幾下個姿勢唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想問係正常酸痛定受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抖一排先，下次再操時做返輕啲，硬拉背要直，郁髖關節用hamstring用屎忽拉，唔係彎腰伸直，操返多啲腳。<br />\n我真係唔係好明點解啲人唔操腳，明明日常生活最具功能性嘅一定係用腳多啲動作，你做得多bench press得嚟嘅成效就係可以做更多bunch press。<br />\n反而腳強壯嘅話，日常跑跳行搬重嘢都好有用</blockquote><br />\n認同<br />\n小妹做gym都花一半時間係腳<br />\n發力好過以前好多</blockquote><br />\n真係會留意下腳 deadlift 半年前做過 依家做就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38449b3c0c287c2b7420350f3e965b7d1fbfaf92","tid":297934,"uid":8097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>受傷<br />\n有機會係拉傷肌肉<br />\n肌肉過緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlower back永遠都要keep住直<br />\n發力點係腳發力先再慢慢到下腰同背<br />\n每一下core都唔可以放鬆 休息一排再做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再痛既話建議你去睇針灸</blockquote><br />\n但係我嗰時做完唔覺痛wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係返到去一排先feel到</blockquote><br />\n小心係腰間盤出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n及早睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"e9e66116aecf8c77cabedb106fcbcde4f23ea2de","tid":297934,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"deadlift係高難度高危動作, 無人睇住好易做錯, 而且無人睇住不宜做太重. <br />\n做得重 要用埋腰封"},{"pid":"047327e18bc89cfeda7d4e948cf118b9c0b55fff","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>受傷<br />\n有機會係拉傷肌肉<br />\n肌肉過緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlower back永遠都要keep住直<br />\n發力點係腳發力先再慢慢到下腰同背<br />\n每一下core都唔可以放鬆 休息一排再做啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再痛既話建議你去睇針灸</blockquote><br />\n但係我嗰時做完唔覺痛wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係返到去一排先feel到</blockquote><br />\n小心係腰間盤出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n及早睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n摸落係痛下背兩側 所以彎唔到身 褲都好難著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個盤反而冇痛"},{"pid":"48eb208122e5763e1eed2d3d7d0e79d0b54cf1db","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>deadlift係高難度高危動作, 無人睇住好易做錯, 而且無人睇住不宜做太重. <br />\n做得重 要用埋腰封</blockquote><br />\n下次做會戴腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當係一次教訓"},{"pid":"424e7f4c3ac08306b0f48daf63b54ab4e639681e","tid":297934,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>deadlift係高難度高危動作, 無人睇住好易做錯, 而且無人睇住不宜做太重. <br />\n做得重 要用埋腰封</blockquote><br />\n下次做會戴腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當係一次教訓</blockquote><br />\n我會建議唔好做deadlift。 <br />\n可以用其他動作代替。<br />\n<br />\n你依家情況要去睇跌打推拿，腰椎軟組織移位"},{"pid":"3923fe7e04ca310f7d86dbede64cda6b9065558a","tid":297934,"uid":30998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:19:44.000Z","msg":"我都係 星期六操完隻腳 依家行個樓梯都痛到仆街"},{"pid":"882a92b819ad3d4ac0d4286d131a8ab40deaeab2","tid":297934,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"deadlift係人體最重要同自然嘅動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做gym唔做deadlift稱唔上functional"},{"pid":"8e8c05c41bf044feefadbc63da981cb142fcaaf4","tid":297934,"uid":8678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:23:29.000Z","msg":"唔識做就 收手 <br />\n唔好格硬  搵人教識你再做"},{"pid":"a67bf5d05d0f8ce36842f5c7bb0f3626fd573eed","tid":297934,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"我第一次做都係咁 應該用錯力<br />\n抖番幾日就冇事<br />\n之後較輕啲 集中用腳發力 就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9006f528cb819c2804052c9bb97d189cc619f2a","tid":297934,"uid":83882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我第一次做都係咁 應該用錯力<br />\n抖番幾日就冇事<br />\n之後較輕啲 集中用腳發力 就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做緊intern 幾日後好返就好 唔想扮工咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}